<body>
<section id="description">
</section>
<ol id="conformance">
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain exactly one [1..1] <tt><b>@classCode</b>="OBS" </tt><i>Observation</i> (CodeSystem:<tt> 2.16.840.1.113883.5.6 HL7ActClass</tt>)
</li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain exactly one [1..1] <tt><b>@moodCode</b>="EVN" </tt><i>Event</i> (CodeSystem:<tt> 2.16.840.1.113883.5.1001 HL7ActMood</tt>)
</li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain at least one [1..*] <tt><b>id</b></tt>
</li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain exactly one [1..1] <tt><b>statusCode</b></tt><tt><b>/@code</b>="completed" </tt> (CodeSystem:<tt> 2.16.840.1.113883.5.14 HL7ActStatus</tt>)
</li>
<li><b>SHOULD</b> contain zero or one [0..1] <tt><b>effectiveTime</b></tt>
</li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain exactly one [1..1] <tt><b>code</b></tt>
</li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain at least one [1..*] <tt><b>advanceDirectiveVerification</b></tt>, such that
<ol>
<li>Contains exactly one [1..1] <xref href="../AdvanceDirectiveVerification.dita">Advance Directive Verification</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.58</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain exactly one [1..1] <tt><b>entryRelationship</b></tt>, such that
<ol>
<li>Contains exactly one [1..1] <xref href="../AdvanceDirectiveStatusObservation.dita">Advance Directive Status Observation</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.37</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain zero or one [0..1] <tt><b>advanceDirectiveReference</b></tt>, such that
<ol>
<li>Contains exactly one [1..1] <xref href="../AdvanceDirectiveReference.dita">Advance Directive Reference</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.36</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li>The value for Observation / code in an advance directive observation <b>MAY</b> be selected from ValueSet 2.16.840.1.113883.1.11.20.2 AdvanceDirectiveTypeCode STATIC 20061017.</li>
<li>There <b>SHOULD</b> be an advance directive observation whose value for Observation / code is '304251008' 'Resuscitation status' 2.16.840.1.113883.6.96 SNOMED CT STATIC</li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> satisfy: Contains one or more sources of information</li>
</ol>
